<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</title>

<style>

/* RESET */
*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
  font-family: system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
  background:#f7f9f8;
  color:#222;
  line-height:1.6;
}

/* HEADER */
.header{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  padding:18px 40px;
  background:#0f6c3f;
  color:#fff;
}

.logo{
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:bold;
}

.nav a{
  margin-left:18px;
  text-decoration:none;
  color:white;
  font-weight:500;
}

.donate-btn{
  background:#ffd54f;
  color:#000;
  padding:8px 14px;
  border-radius:6px;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  height:85vh;
  background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.5), rgba(0,0,0,.5)),
  url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588072432836-e10032774350?q=80&w=1200") center/cover no-repeat;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  text-align:center;
  color:white;
}

.hero h1{
  font-size:42px;
  margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
  max-width:600px;
  margin:auto;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.main-btn{
  background:#ffd54f;
  color:black;
  padding:12px 28px;
  text-decoration:none;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-weight:bold;
}

/* ABOUT */
.about-short{
  padding:70px 20px;
  text-align:center;
  background:white;
}

.secondary-btn{
  display:inline-block;
  margin-top:15px;
  padding:10px 20px;
  border:2px solid #0f6c3f;
  color:#0f6c3f;
  text-decoration:none;
  border-radius:6px;
}

/* SERVICES */
.services{
  padding:70px 20px;
  text-align:center;
}

.service-box{
  background:white;
  padding:25px;
  margin:20px auto;
  max-width:320px;
  border-radius:12px;
  box-shadow:0 5px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

/* IMPACT */
.impact{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:40px;
  padding:70px 20px;
  background:#eef4f1;
}

.impact-box{
  text-align:center;
}

.impact-box h3{
  font-size:36px;
  color:#0f6c3f;
}

/* DONATION HELP */
.donation-help{
  padding:70px 20px;
  text-align:center;
  background:white;
}

.donation-help li{
  margin:10px 0;
  font-size:18px;
  list-style:none;
}

/* CTA */
.cta{
  background:#0f6c3f;
  color:white;
  text-align:center;
  padding:70px 20px;
}

/* FOOTER */
.footer{
  background:#111;
  color:#ddd;
  text-align:center;
  padding:25px;
  font-size:14px;
}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .hero h1{font-size:28px;}
  .impact{flex-direction:column;}
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="header">
  <div class="logo">Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</div>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#" class="donate-btn">Donate</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <h1>Ek Paul Shikshanasaathi</h1>
    <p>तुमचं एक छोटंसं पाऊल, एखाद्या मुलाचं संपूर्ण भविष्य घडवू शकतं.</p>
    <a href="#" class="main-btn">Donate Now</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-short">
  <h2>About The Initiative</h2>
  <p>गरिब मुलांना शिक्षणाची मदत देण्याचा सामाजिक उपक्रम.</p>
  <a href="#" class="secondary-btn">Read More</a>
</section>

<section class="services">
  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <div class="service-box">शैक्षणिक साहित्य</div>
  <div class="service-box">फी सहाय्य</div>
  <div class="service-box">पूर्ण शिक्षण समर्थन</div>
</section>

<section class="impact">
  <div class="impact-box"><h3>50+</h3><p>Students</p></div>
  <div class="impact-box"><h3>200+</h3><p>Books</p></div>
  <div class="impact-box"><h3>10+</h3><p>Schools</p></div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <h2>आजच एक पाऊल टाका</h2>
  <p>Support a child's education</p>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <p>Yashasvi Foundation</p>
  <p>Founders: Pankaj Gunjal & Gitesh Ahire</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
